commit.message:
Add RPC equivalence tests for the crypto functions.

For hstox tests, these are trivial and only check whether the msgpack encoding
is correct. For toxcore tests, these help identify functions in which toxcore
and hstox behave differently.

Add RPC equivalence tests for the crypto functions.

For hstox tests, these are trivial and only check whether the msgpack encoding
is correct. For toxcore tests, these help identify functions in which toxcore
and hstox behave differently.
